generateInBatch: Generate RGs, input below the quantity of documents you wish. Select 'With mask' if wish to generate documents with mask

ariaLabels.withMaskCheckbox: Checkbox to decide if generates RG data with mask or without mask
ariaLabels.generateButton: Button with an icon which has the action to generate the RG
ariaLabels.generateWithMaskButton: Button with an icon which has the action to generate the RG with mask
